snippet.title: Beat Academy
snippet.description:
Beat Academy is the place to learn music production from credible music producers.

Founded by Grammy-nominated producer Ivan Corraliza, professionally known as ill Factor, you'll learn the techniques and strategies for music production used by the biggest producers and artists in the industry.

ill Factor has been producing music for more than eighteen years, working on projects with: Justin Timberlake, Sia, Kygo, Jason Derulo, Skylar Grey, Ginuwine, Kelly Rowland, Kevin Rudolf, Cher, Jessie J, Groove Armada, Calvin Harris and many others.


Visit: https://www.beatacademy.com
Instagram: @illfactor
Twitter: @illfactor
